      <title>鲍威尔称美联储需要对通胀更有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/powell-to-say-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔将向立法者重申，在政策制定者确信他们已经赢得了对抗通胀的战斗之前，美国央行并不急于降息。迈克·麦基报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/powell-to-say-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国推出 2650 亿英镑债券销售计划，减少长期债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/uk-to-sell-265-billion-debt-broadly-matching-market-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府宣布了下一财年的借贷计划，基本符合市场预期，同时将销售进一步远离长期债券，以应对证券兴趣减弱的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/uk-to-sell-265-billion-debt-broadly-matching-market-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:47:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
